title: Legend of Zelda: Ocarina of Time ROM+Hi-Res texture pack
description:
This is The Legend of Zelda: Ocarina of Time N64 Rom (good dump) with the latest known K-Man/Xenobond + Federelli Hi-Res Texture mod work available, plus the addition of other hi-res textures gathered from different sources. It is the most complete hi-res texture pack for this game around.

Also included are Mudlord's Rice Video plugin and the Glide64 'Napalm' v1.0 plugin which is said to work with texture mods and widescreen.

Designed to work with Project64 v 1.6.

Installation Instructions:
-extract the archive directly to Project64 installation folder. Everything is ready to go.
-optional: Move the ROM to your own ROM directory. It is included in the default directory.

Check the readme for further info.

Enjoy!

kylezo
